---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Você é Novo Aqui? - 1IPIM" isImmersive={true}>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 relative w-full h-[100svh] min-h-[600px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-colors overflow-hidden border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[var(--color-success)]/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[var(--color-brand)]/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl text-center relative z-10" id="fadeDiv">
            <h1 class="font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight select-none">
                Olá! Nós amamos <br><span class="text-[var(--color-success)]">receber visitantes.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-2xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Sabemos que ir a uma nova igreja pela primeira vez pode ser intimidante. Preparamos esse guia rápido para você descobrir o que esperar de um domingo conosco.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Scroll indicator -->
        <a aria-label="Role para baixo" href="#conteudo" class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center animate-bounce text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 hover:text-[var(--color-success)] select-none hidden lg:flex cursor-pointer no-underline transition-colors z-20">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down text-3xl"></i>
        </a>
    </header>

    <section id="conteudo" class="py-24 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl">
            
            <!-- O que Esperar (Grid 3) -->
            <div class="mb-20">
                <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 scroll-card">
                    <h2 class="font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">O que você vai encontrar?</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg">A identidade dos nossos cultos gira em torno destes pilares essenciais.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-10 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 scroll-card flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[var(--color-brand)]/10 rounded-full blur-[50px] pointer-events-none group-hover:bg-[var(--color-brand)]/20 transition-colors"></div>
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-brand)]/10 text-[var(--color-brand)] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform relative z-10">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-hands-praying"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-extrabold text-2xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 relative z-10">Louvor Reverente</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-900 dark:group-hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors relative z-10">
                            Nós cantamos a Palavra de Deus. Nossas músicas unem a profundidade dos hinos tradicionais à vibração dos louvores contemporâneos, sempre com o foco exclusivo em exaltar a Cristo e não a nós mesmos.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-10 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 scroll-card flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-[50px] pointer-events-none group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-colors"></div>
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform relative z-10">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-book-open"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-extrabold text-2xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 relative z-10">Pregação Expositiva</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-900 dark:group-hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors relative z-10">
                            Cremos na exposição fiel das Escrituras. Nossos sermões abrem a Bíblia de passagem em passagem, extraindo a sã doutrina e a aplicando de forma totalmente prática e transformadora ao seu dia-a-dia.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-10 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 scroll-card flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-32 h-32 bg-orange-500/10 rounded-full blur-[50px] pointer-events-none group-hover:bg-orange-500/20 transition-colors"></div>
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform relative z-10">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-mug-hot"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-extrabold text-2xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 relative z-10">Comunhão Genuína</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-900 dark:group-hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors relative z-10">
                            Somos pessoas reais e imperfeitas que foram alcançadas pela Graça. Após o culto, nosso balcão de café ferve de abraços, conversas sinceras e braços abertos para te incluir em nossa família na fé.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Playlist 1 IPI - Spotify -->
            <div class="mb-20 scroll-card">
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch">
                    <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center lg:w-2/5">
                        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#1DB954]/10 text-[#1DB954] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full w-max mb-5">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-spotify"></i> Spotify
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-extrabold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 leading-tight">Conheça nossos louvores antes de chegar</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Que tal já se familiarizar com as músicas que cantamos no culto? Nossa playlist oficial está disponível no Spotify para você ouvir onde e quando quiser.</p>
                        <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5AN5riUaqUQzKYlm0bAo6I" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#1DB954] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-sm hover:bg-[#17a349] transition-colors shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 w-max">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-spotify"></i> Ouvir Playlist 1 IPI
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:w-3/5 min-h-[352px]">
                        <iframe
                            src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/5AN5riUaqUQzKYlm0bAo6I?utm_source=generator&theme=0"
                            width="100%" height="352"
                            frameborder="0"
                            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
                            loading="lazy"
                            style="display:block;"
                        ></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Kids & Locais (2 Cards lado a lado) -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-20">
                <!-- Kids -->
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1cb0f6] to-[#0d7cae] rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-12 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow text-white scroll-card relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 text-white/10 text-9xl group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-700 pointer-events-none">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shapes"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-center">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                            <span class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xl shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-child text-white"></i>
                            </span>
                            <span class="font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm bg-black/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Ministério Infantil</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6 leading-tight drop-shadow-md">Seus filhos estão em ótimas mãos!</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-0 font-medium max-w-lg">
                            Durante todos os nossos cultos de domingo, as crianças têm o seu próprio momento. Elas recebem ensino bíblico seguro, alegre e dinâmico adequado à linguagem infantil, enquanto os pais podem adorar a Deus profundamente na nave principal sem preocupações.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Locais -->
                <a href="/contato" class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 scroll-card relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col group">
                    <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-64 h-64 bg-[var(--color-success)]/5 rounded-full blur-[80px] pointer-events-none group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
                    
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-success)]/10 text-[var(--color-success)] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-8 shadow-sm group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight">Onde nos<br/>reunimos?</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-1">
                        Além da nossa sede no centro de Machado, possuímos diversas congregações abrangendo vários bairros e cidades vizinhas. Você certamente descobrirá uma Primeira IPIM bem perto do seu lar.
                    </p>
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 font-extrabold text-[var(--color-success)] text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-2">
                        Ver nossos endereços <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQs Grid -->
            <div class="mb-20">
                <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 scroll-card">
                    <h2 class="font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Dúvidas Frequentes</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg">Respondemos as principais perguntas de quem chega pela primeira vez.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <!-- FAQ 1 -->
                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow scroll-card h-full flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden group">
                        <div class="absolute -right-6 -top-6 text-gray-100 dark:text-slate-800 text-7xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 pointer-events-none z-0"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 relative z-10">Que horas chego?</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed relative z-10 flex-1">
                            Nosso culto principal de celebração acontece aos <strong>Domingos às 19h</strong>. Recomendamos chegar alguns minutinhos antes. Assim, dá tempo de estacionar com calma e bater um bom papo no saguão antes da adoração iniciar.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ 2 -->
                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow scroll-card h-full flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden group">
                        <div class="absolute -right-6 -top-6 text-gray-100 dark:text-slate-800 text-7xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 pointer-events-none z-0"><i class="fa-solid fa-shirt"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 relative z-10">O que devo vestir?</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed relative z-10 flex-1">
                            Apenas venha como você se sente bem. Não cobramos nenhum tipo de "dress code". Sentado ao seu lado poderá haver pessoas de terno ou pessoas de jeans e tênis; o que nos importa profundamente é o seu coração e a sua presença conosco!
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ 3 -->
                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow scroll-card h-full flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden group">
                        <div class="absolute -right-6 -top-6 text-gray-100 dark:text-slate-800 text-7xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 pointer-events-none z-0"><i class="fa-solid fa-wallet"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 relative z-10">Sou obrigado a ofertar?</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed relative z-10 flex-1">
                            <strong>De maneira nenhuma.</strong> O momento da oferta litúrgica é voltado para os membros frequentadores da casa que adoram devolvendo sistematicamente aquilo que Deus proveu. Sendo visitante, considere-se cordialmente como nosso convidado sem obrigações.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ 4 -->
                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow scroll-card h-full flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden group">
                        <div class="absolute -right-6 -top-6 text-gray-100 dark:text-slate-800 text-7xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 pointer-events-none z-0"><i class="fa-solid fa-wine-glass"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 relative z-10">Posso participar da Santa Ceia?</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed relative z-10 flex-1">
                            A Santa Ceia, um sacramento sublime, é voltada estritamente aos cristãos crentes professos que já foram batizados em Cristo e encontram-se em comunhão perante o Senhor e suas igrejas locais (mesmo vindos de outras denominações evangélicas).
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA Final -->
            <div class="text-center scroll-card relative overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-16 shadow-xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto group hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#25D366]/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none group-hover:from-[#25D366]/20 transition-colors duration-500"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#25D366]/20 text-[#25D366] flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mx-auto mb-6 shadow-none group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 relative z-10">Ainda pintou alguma dúvida?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto relative z-10">Nossa equipe de recepção adoraria conversar com você. Basta nos dar um "Oi" no WhatsApp!</p>
                <a href="https://wa.me/5535988613046" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-[#25D366] text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-extrabold hover:bg-[#128C7E] transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 justify-center text-lg active:scale-95">
                    Mandar mensagem agora
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
